tool_description: Get music data from freepd.com (scraping), list of more than 800 royalty-free music.
title: FreePD

api_list.name: NUMBERED PAGE
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://freepd.p.rapidapi.com/p/{page}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "freepd.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
